00:32:03.650 --> 00:32:04.560
Hindi mo nakita

00:32:04.560 --> 00:32:06.110
kung gaano kalakas ang tiwala ni He Xian

00:32:06.110 --> 00:32:07.460
noong kinausap niya tayo!

00:32:08.200 --> 00:32:09.330
Kung hindi nagising si Asahina,

00:32:09.330 --> 00:32:10.220
hindi ba't ang kasinungalingan

00:32:10.220 --> 00:32:11.630
nalantad
noong pumunta roon si Imai?

00:32:11.630 --> 00:32:12.430
Sa tingin mo ba ay si He Xian?

00:32:12.430 --> 00:32:13.630
magsasabi ng ganito kalaking kasinungalingan?

00:32:13.630 --> 00:32:14.780
Maglalakas-loob kaya siya?

00:32:14.930 --> 00:32:17.150
Nagpapadala na sila ng pagkain!

00:32:17.150 --> 00:32:19.680
Nakakita ka na ba
ng taong walang malay na kumakain?

00:32:22.190 --> 00:32:24.090
Walang Tapang na Biao, huwag mong kalimutan.

00:32:27.430 --> 00:32:29.440
Ito ay ang sarili mong kawalang-ingat

00:32:30.390 --> 00:32:32.150
na nagbigay-daan kay Asahina-hina na makita ang iyong mukha,

00:32:32.150 --> 00:32:32.800
tama?

00:32:33.670 --> 00:32:34.500
Tama?

00:32:36.150 --> 00:32:37.800
