00:35:21.850 --> 00:35:22.980
Simulan agad.

00:35:25.290 --> 00:35:26.410
Walang pagpipilian kung gayon.

00:35:26.580 --> 00:35:27.450
Umakyat ka sa taas,

00:35:27.450 --> 00:35:28.850
